text: Bought the Seafood Kampong Fried Rice. The best fried rice I had in the last few months. For the price, it was worth it. Reasonable quantity of seafood ingredients and the dish was overall tasty and satisfying.

Hands down, this Seafood Tom Yum Fried Rice is on point! A good amount of aromatic rice mixed with a decent amount of seafood served alongside crunchy crackers, which gives it a good crunch. A must visit and a must place to return!

Take away from this stall a few times already.

The sambal stingray, quite good, well grilled and tasty. Kangkong was not bad as well.

The other thing I tried was hor fun which is average.
